  <name>XML Copy Editor</name>
  <summary>Fast, free, validating XML editor</summary>
  
  <description>
    <p>
      XML Copy Editor is an XML editor focusing on editing document markup
      languages like DITA, DocBook, and WordprocessingML. It provides a fast
      and intuitive interface for creating and editing XML documents with
      validation support.
    </p>
    <p>
      Key features:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>DTD/XML Schema/RELAX NG validation</li>
      <li>XSLT and XPath support</li>
      <li>Pretty-printing and syntax highlighting</li>
      <li>Element folding for better navigation</li>
      <li>Tag completion and tag locking</li>
      <li>Tag-free editing mode</li>
      <li>Built-in support for XHTML, XSL, DocBook and TEI</li>
      <li>XML Schema generation</li>
      <li>Spell checking with Enchant</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
  <launchable type="desktop-id">net.sourceforge.xmlcopyeditor.desktop</launchable>
  
